    dc:description "Figure 7. Ooencyrtus mirus sp. nov. female A holotype slide B antenna (holotype) C head in frontal view (paratype) D mesosoma (holotype) E mesosoma and metasoma (holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/404427" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.76.48004.figure8>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Ooencyrtus mirus sp. nov. A female fore and hind wings (holotype) B male habitus in lateral view (paratype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/404428" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.76.48004.figure9>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Ooencyrtus mirus sp. nov. male (paratypes) A antenna B fore wing C genitalia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/404429" ;
