<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.76.48004.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Ooencyrtus telenomicida female (from Romania) A habitus in lateral view (neotype, prior to DNA extraction) B habitus in dorsal view (non-type) C mesosoma and metasoma (neotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/404430" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.76.48004.figure12>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Ooencyrtus telenomicida female A habitus in lateral view (from Nikolaevskaya oblast', Ukraine) B habitus in dorsolateral view (from Krasnodarskiy kray, Russia) C antenna (from Stavropol'skiy kray, Russia)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/404432" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.76.48004.figure13>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Ooencyrtus telenomicida (from Stavropol'skiy kray, Russia) A female head in frontal view B male genitalia C female mesosoma and metasoma D female fore wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/404433" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.76.48004.figure16>
    dc:description "Figure 16. Multivariate ratio analysis for Ooencyrtus mirus sp. nov. and O. telenomicida A scatterplot of isosize against first shape PC B shape PCA, scatterplot of first against second shape PC C PCA ratio spectrum for PC 1, bars represent 68 % confidence intervals D allometry ratio spectrum; bars represent 68 % confidence intervals." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/404436" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

